parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering linkage can cause the vehicle to violently shake and become difficult to control, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle's front end shakes violently
the steering wheel vibrates or jerks
the vehicle becomes difficult to control
and the driver may experience a loss of steering control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the vehicle to become difficult to steer, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The power steering fails without warning
the steering wheel becomes difficult to turn
the vehicle becomes hard to steer
and the driver may experience a loss of steering control.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Delays in recall repairs can leave vehicles on the road with known safety defects, increasing the risk of accidents and injuries.
symptoms: Dealerships are unable to perform recall repairs due to parts unavailability
leaving vehicles with safety defects on the road.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unintended Movement of Vehicle from Park
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle can move unexpectedly from park, causing accidents, injuries, or property damage.
symptoms: The vehicle moves on its own from park
sometimes into reverse
without the driver's input.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The transmission fails to shift properly
causing the vehicle to stall or lose power
or the transmission slips or hesitates when shifting.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transfer case failure can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The transfer case fails
causing the vehicle to lose power or become stuck in four-wheel drive mode.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Differential failure can cause loss of vehicle control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: The differential fails
causing the vehicle to vibrate or shake
or the wheels to lock up.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The out-of-park alarm can be annoying and distracting, and may not provide adequate warning in certain situations.
symptoms: The out-of-park alarm sounds unnecessarily or fails to sound when the vehicle is not in park.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Takata airbag inflator can cause serious injury or death due to metal fragments striking vehicle occupants.
symptoms: None reported
as the issue is related to a potential failure of the airbag inflator.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning indicator can indicate a potential problem with the airbag system, which can lead to accidents or injuries if not addressed.
symptoms: Airbag warning indicator illuminates on the dashboard.
